erlang-indira (1.0.0-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Improvements in AF_UNIX sockets (support for longer lines, auto-unlinking
    on BEAM crash, setting permissions and ownership of listening sockets).
  * Major API reorganization
    - functions from indira_app and indira_cli modules moved elsewhere
    - stabilized interface for configuring applications
    - module for reading from STDIN
    - other minor changes

 -- Stanislaw Klekot <dozzie@jarowit.net>  Sat, 28 Oct 2017 17:03:42 +0200

